            "questionText": "An intergalactic cargo ship is transporting a piece of equipment with a mass of $!$150\\,\\text{kg}$!$. On Earth, the gravitational field strength is $!$9.8\\,\\text{N/kg}$!$, and on Mars, it is $!$3.7\\,\\text{N/kg}$!$. Calculate the absolute difference in the equipment's weight on Earth compared to its weight on Mars.",
